 <refsect1 id="package.versioncontrol.hg.versioncontrol-hg-executable.--construct.desc">
  &title.desc;
  <para>Finds and sets the system&apos;s existing Mercurial executable binary which  with all future operations will use.</para>
 </refsect1>
